title: Sparc
description: Virtual Sport. Real Competition.Sparcs a vSport - a unique physical sport only possible in virtual reality, in which players compete in fast-paced, full-body VR gameplay and connect in an online community. Compete online in one-on-one multiplayer matches against friends or via matchmaking Practice your skills by testing yourself in single-player challenges and trials Customize your avatar with a wide variety of visually striking and attention-grabbing options Watch matches in-person and queue
